HEADWORD: Scutch grass
<hw>Scutch" grass`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A kind of
pasture grass (<spn>Cynodon Dactylon</spn>). See <er>Bermuda grass</er>:
also <xex>Illustration</xex> in Appendix.</def>⟦br⟧
